title: [K.o.R] Takeshi's Castle - Season 4 (Complete - 22/22)
description:
After what seems like an age, I finally obtained the 3 missing episodes, meaning that Season 4 is now complete. The old torrent will be deleted in a couple of days; everyone should switch to this torrent ASAP.

File Format: Matroska MKV
Video Codec: h264 AVC
Audio Codec: AAC

**FOR USERS OF THE OLD TORRENT**

The two "unaired" episodes were 403 and 404, meaning that all episode numbers from the existing 403 onward need to be increased by two in order to be able to resume the old torrent on this one.

For example,

[K.o.R] Takeshi's Castle - 403 [h264][AAC][607C459F].mkv

in the old batch will become

[K.o.R] Takeshi's Castle - 405 [h264][AAC][607C459F].mkv

in the new batch. Check and match up the CRCs in the new batch if you are not sure. Hopefully 2 minutes of renaming will save you from ~2 gigs of unnecessary re-downloading!

Enjoy, and please help seed when you are done!
